OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FEx-Tory councillor         
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fdiscriminated against,     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Freport says                
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A former Conservative councillor was   
OL,6, repeatedly discriminated against on the
OL,7, basis of his Muslim faith or Pakistani 
OL,8, background, a confidential independent 
OL,9, report has found.                      
OL,11,FMohammed Arif, a Walsall councillor,   
OL,12,Fclaimed he was blocked from standing   
OL,13,Ffor re-election by the local party in  
OL,14,F2015 and discriminated against.        
OL,16,FHe said he had not received an "open   
OL,17,Fand frank" apology from the party.     
OL,19,FA Conservative Party spokesperson said 
OL,20,Fthey were unable to comment.           
